notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-21T14:46:52.517Z",claude-code-agent,"Implemented in src/sdk/testing.ts (+ barrel src/sdk/index.ts). Added 6 invoke helpers completing the command-pipeline \"invoke\" verb symmetric to runRegisteredCommandForTest (pm-owm0): runRegisteredHookForTest (5 lifecycle kinds via a type-safe discriminated-union RunRegisteredHookForTestOptions; returns runner warnings, [] = clean; throws listing populated kinds when none of the requested kind exist) + runRegistered{Parser,Preflight,Command,Renderer,Service}OverrideForTest (each guards a matching override is registered for the target command/format/service — preflight guards non-empty since the runtime applies the last override regardless of command — then delegates to the real runtime runner and returns the *OverrideResult verbatim). All async for a uniform await API. Reused existing HOOK_KIND_TO_REGISTRY_FIELD map + normalizeSdkCommandName/sortedUnique/formatAvailable helpers (no new private helpers). Runtime runners + context/result types imported from core/extensions/loader.js (re-exported there via export * from extension-types.js). 100% coverage of testing.ts (348/348 stmts, 268/268 branch, 119/119 func). Manual E2E in temp dir against built dist: all 9 checks (clean hook, warning hook, hook guard, 5 override invokes, override guard) passed. Docs: SDK.md export list + invoke-verb paragraph + Testing Helpers examples; EXTENSIONS.md one-line note (kept under 450-line cap)."
